Update the pom.xml with this plugin in the `<build><plugins>` section:

```xml
<plugin>
    <groupId>pl.project13.maven</groupId>
    <artifactId>git-commit-id-plugin</artifactId>
    <version>${maven-plugin-git-commit-id.version}</version>
    <executions>
